headline.print_headline: Australia's Lehmann Pleased to Be 'Bowled Out'
headline.main: Australia's Lehmann Pleased to Be 'Bowled Out'

lead_paragraph: Australia's dramatic collapse against South Africa at the weekend has drawn inevitable comparisons with their previous test defeat but vanquished coach Darren Lehmann says the two losses were vastly different.
